Hearing the message Kenzo flew away from Flicker. Kenzo loaded in the
wounded maximal into his copter form using robotic arms that extended
out the doors of the copter. He flew aways until he reached the
Maximal base.  While in transit his internal repair systems were able
to administer minor repairs like a lesser version of the CR chamber. 
He landed in front of the base and carefully unloaded them onto the
ground. He converted to robot mode.

OOC: I hope flying away from Flicker all the way to the base wasn't
moding but my guy was getting behind.  Also who were the two maximals
Kenzo needed to transport?
